        "text": "The Angular app bootstraps `AppComponent` with `appConfig`; `appConfig` provides router, NgRx playlist/router state, effects, translations, IndexedDB configuration, service worker registration, environment-specific `DataService`, portal playback/navigation tokens, workspace shell actions, and the Xtream data-source provider.",
